  <h3>Permissions</h3> 
  <p>Permissions give users and groups access to AEM functionality on AEM pages.</p> 
  <p>You browse permissions by path by expanding/collapsing the nodes and you can track the permission inheritance up to the root node.<br /> </p> 
  <p>You allow or deny permissions by selecting or clearing the appropriate check boxes.</p> 
