  <p>In addition to viewing information, you can also include or exclude the current user or group from a group. See <a href="#addingusersorgroupswhileaddingpermissions">Adding Users or Groups while Adding Permissions</a>. Changes made here are immediately reflected in the upper portion of the detailed view.<br /> </p> 
